Your Honor Jokes &ldquo;But your honor, I only purchased those five hundred pounds of fertilizer because it tastes so damn good!&rdquo;
&ldquo;Your honor, I know I&rsquo;m on the no - fly list, but I was clearly wearing basketball shorts.&rdquo;
&ldquo;Your honor, I sincerely apologize. I merely forgot that armed robbery is illegal.&rdquo;
&ldquo;Your honor, I know the light was red, but I only turned the right way.&rdquo;
&ldquo;Your honor, have a little respect! I spent the better part of two months working on that thing. Calling it an &lsquo;improvized&rsquo; explosive is just insulting.&rdquo;
&ldquo;No, your honor, I didn&rsquo;t really mind that she got the kids. What pushed me over the edge is how she took the air fryer.&rdquo;
&ldquo;Your honor, I assure you that he put those cement shoes on his own feet, shot himself in the back of the head, and lept into the lake of his own accord.&rdquo;
&ldquo;Your honor, I was innocent by reason of insanity. You would be too if you had to live with him.&rdquo;
