Math Problem Thirty-Nine: Cornpop is a Bad Dude Jack and his crew steal Elon Musk&rsquo;s fastest UFO and return once more to the Earth. They land on Jeffery Epstein&rsquo;s island - now restored to its previous glory - to find Joe Biden and Bill Clinton standing in front of the door.
&ldquo;What the hell kid?&rdquo; asks Bill Clinton. &ldquo;I thought you died!&rdquo;
&ldquo;I was once slain, but now I live. I am Jack, conqueror of death!&rdquo;
Bill is about to respond, but he&rsquo;s cut off by the other archon.
&ldquo;Shabapaduba?&rdquo; Joe Biden questions, gesturing vaguely towards Kaegan with a befuddled expression on his face. &ldquo;I-I coulda sworn, man. That right there is Corn Pop! He&rsquo;s a bad dude, usedta run a buncha bad boys&hellip;&rdquo;
Kaegan throws up his hands. &ldquo;I don&rsquo;t know bro. I ain&rsquo;t named Corn Pop. There are 8 billion people in the world and only one corn pop. I probably ain&rsquo;t him.&rdquo;
Biden grows angry and begins foaming at the mouth. &ldquo;Come on man! You ain&rsquo;t black, you lying, dog - faced pony soldier! You&rsquo;re a Corn Pop &lsquo;cause I says you&rsquo;re a Corn Pop!&rdquo; The politician throws his head back in anger and thrusts forwards his right hand. &ldquo;BIDEN BLAST!&rdquo; he screams in fury, causing a blue pulse of energy to arc between his hand and Kaegan, - reducing the later to a pile of ashes.
&ldquo;No!&rdquo; Screams Hayden. &ldquo;They killed Kaegan!&rdquo;
&ldquo;You bastards!&rdquo; I echo.
Fury begins rising in Jack&rsquo;s bosom, fury like he&rsquo;s never felt before. His eyes glow red with wrath - the wrath of the god emperor of mankind. The Earth begins to shake and thunder roles. &ldquo;Lɪsᴛᴇɴ ᴜᴘ, sᴏᴄɪᴀʟɪsᴛ sᴄᴜᴍ!&rdquo; outpours an otherworldly, ferocious voice quite unlike his own. &ldquo;Yᴏᴜ&rsquo;ᴠᴇ ᴋɪʟʟᴇᴅ Kᴇᴀɢᴀɴ, ʙᴜᴛ ʜᴇ ᴡᴀsɴ&rsquo;ᴛ ᴛʜᴇ ꜰɪʀsᴛ! I ᴋɴᴏᴡ ᴛʜᴇ ʜɪsᴛᴏʀʏ ᴏꜰ ʏᴏᴜʀ sᴏᴄɪᴀʟɪsᴍ! I ᴋɴᴏᴡ ᴛʜᴇ ᴡᴏʀᴅs ʏᴏᴜ ᴄᴀɴ&rsquo;ᴛ sᴛᴀɴᴅ ᴛᴏ ʜᴇᴀʀ, ᴛʜᴇ ᴡᴏʀᴅs ᴛʜᴀᴛ ᴇxᴏʀᴄɪsᴇ ᴀɴʏ ʟɪʙᴇʀᴀʟ ғʀᴏᴍ ᴛʜɪs ᴍᴏʀᴛᴀʟ ᴘʟᴀɴᴇ!
&ldquo;ɪPʜᴏɴᴇ! &hellip;
&hellip; Vᴇɴᴇᴢᴜᴇʟᴀ! &hellip;
&hellip; ONE HUNDRED &hellip;
&hellip; UNDECILLION &hellip;
&hellip; DDDEEEAAADDD!!!!&rdquo;
The fiends cover their ears, trying to shield themselves from those fateful, ruinous words. But, it is to no avail. They begin screeching in pain, and soon are melting away like the Nazis at the end of Indiana Jones and the Raiders of the Lost Ark.
Jack sighs. &ldquo;Another cuck leftist destroyed.&rdquo;
&hellip;
If socialism killed 100 undecillion people, as Jack proved with facts and logic, and there are 8 billion people in the world right now (as Kaegan stated), then how many orders of magnitude more people has socialism killed then are alive today?
&lt;== Back to Math Problems Home Page &lt;==

Math Problem Thirty-Eight: Tesla Man - Least of the Archons At the crack of Philip&rsquo;s whip, Star in the Morning Sky begins lumbering forwards on her borderline defunct legs. As she reaches 8.8 miles per hour, Jack and his company enter the tunnel of light once more. As they go forward, Jack ceases to be the disembodied ghost he has been, and finds himself arrayed as the god - emperor of mankind once more. His triceps swell, he gains the abs of an anime tomboy, and golden armor covers his body.
&ldquo;Wait, something&rsquo;s wrong!&rdquo; Philip declares with manly yet apprehensive perturbance. &ldquo;Earth isn&rsquo;t up ahead! This darned horse is taking us to the moon!&rdquo;
But, before Philip can stop anything, the tunnel of light vanishes, and the carriage grinds to a halt on solid, firmly material ground. Jack closes his eyes, expecting to die like an imposter thrown out of the airlock. But, he doesn&rsquo;t. He breathes in and slowly opens his eyes, finding himself still very much alive.
They step outside the carriage to find themselves in a hideous moon base, made entirely of plastic - exactly like every generic spaceship on TV.
&ldquo;What the hell is going on! Wikipedia doesn&rsquo;t say anything about there being a base like this on the moon!&rdquo; says Jimmy Wales.
A strange, A.I. generated cackling sounds behind them. &ldquo;Ha. Ha. Ha. You are fools.&rdquo;
Jack turns around wildly and draws his sword, but he only sees an expensive - looking Tesla car. But then, its parts begin shifting into a new form - the form of a huge man made of plastic and steel.
&ldquo;Like zoinks! It&rsquo;s a transformer!&rdquo; Shaggy proclaims.
&ldquo;Before my augmentation, I was called Elon Musk, and I am the least of the archons. How dare you trespass on my moon base?&rdquo;
&ldquo;Wait, this is totally fake!&rdquo; I say. &ldquo;How come no one found this place when people went to the moon? There has to be a naturalistic explanation for this.&rdquo;
&ldquo;No, no one ever went to the moon. This is where UFOs hail from, and it has been so since the time of the ancient Egyptians. To keep the mortals from discovering them, they were forbidden from coming to the moon.&rdquo;
Just as I am about to respond, Jimmy Wales jumps into action and begins doing battle with Elon Musk - quoting negative statistics about spaceX and Tesla all the while. The fight is long, hard, and brutal. But, in the end, the African American businessman falls to his knees in subjection.
&ldquo;No! You may have defeated me, but you cannot defeat the other archons! You are on the road to destruction! All of your base are belong to us! The others are gathered at Jeffry Epstein&rsquo;s island, and they will summon the antichrist in 37 minutes, bringing about the end times. My fastest UFO will get you there in 27 minutes. How long, pray tell, will that leave you to fight them?&rdquo;
&lt;== Back to Math Problems Home Page &lt;==

Math Problem Thirty-Seven: The Deepest Pit of Heck Jack and his compatriots steel themselves for what&rsquo;s ahead, for they know the next circle of Heck is deepest and darkest one, home to the greatest of sinners. It is the place where the soul Jack must rescue for his quest is said to dwell.
But, when they get there, they&rsquo;re pleasantly surprised. It just looks like a bar. Some lit EDM beats are playing in the background, and the stench of beer can be detected everywhere. And &hellip;
Oh.
There are many sensuous, scantily - clad succubi gyrating atop the tables. It&rsquo;s not just a bar, it&rsquo;s a strip club!
&ldquo;Woah.&rdquo; says Keagan. &ldquo;I&rsquo;m not like, down bad for the forces of darkness or anything, but them succubi are downright callipygian.&rdquo;
Jack sees two people he knew in life: Jimmy Wales and his old pal Alvin McGee. Both of them are sitting at a table, ogling a particularly voluptuous succubus of Korean extraction.
&ldquo;Yo, Al, Jimmy Wales, why is this circle of Heck so fun? Isn&rsquo;t it supposed to be like for the worst of the worst?&rdquo;
&ldquo;Oh, hey Jack,&rsquo; I say, taking my eyes of off my favored succubus for a second. &ldquo;Well, this circle of Heck sucked for a long time. The archangel Samael was ordered to create it in order to house truly grave sinners, like rapists and NIMBYs. It was supposed to be based on the sadistic fantasies some religious people had about what would happen to their enemies in the afterlife, all that stuff you find in Dante&rsquo;s Inferno, The Apocalypse of Peter, and some of Tertullian and Arthur Pink&rsquo;s writings on the subject. There were people liquefying in flames, guys being hung from the roof by their testicles, everybody being eaten by worms, something about a girl being painted blue. It was horrible!
&ldquo;But then a bunch of people realized all that was evil balderdash, so C.S. Lewis invented this idea where Heck is just voluntary separation from God! He published a book about this in 1945, and then 10% of people came to agree with him per decade. When this more humane portrait of eternal &ldquo;punishment&rdquo; came to predominate in the popular imagination, the gates of this circle of Heck became locked from the inside.
&ldquo;But, that meant old Sammie needed to invent a reason for people not to leave (Saint Peter would be very angry if all these supposedly sequestered sinners just showed up in Heaven demanding to be left in. Nobody wants a postmortem refugee crisis!. So, after sleeping on it, the good angel hired the succubi to make this circle a bit more appealing to its inhabitants. After all, everyone in Heck has an unreasonably strong libido and there ain&rsquo;t no sex in Heaven, so nobody who was sent here has ever left (a couple of them tried before they heard about the renovations, but the good archangel flagged them down on the road to Heaven and said something along the lines of &ldquo;please come back, there are boobs now. I heard you liked boobs.&rdquo;)
None of the women were fooled by this, not even the ones who were into girls in the first place, but almost every man in this circle happily took Samael up on his offer.
&ldquo;Philip, calculate what year everything changed.&rdquo;
&ldquo;Wait, before I have to do the math on that,&rdquo; begins Philip, who apparently became rather knowledgable about theology while in Limbo, &ldquo;how do Christians who believe in annihilationism or purgatorial universalism, like the church fathers Saints Theophilus of Antioch and Gregory of Nyssa respectively, fit into this calculation of yours?&rdquo;
&ldquo;See,&rdquo; I respond, &ldquo;Pastor Jim says they were postmodern neomarxist libtards, and hence fake Christians.&rdquo;
&ldquo;Oh okay,&rdquo; Jack says, &ldquo;but I gotta ask, why are you here and how&rsquo;d you get here? I know Jimmy was a terrible person and I killed him, but Al, you&rsquo;re just a normal guy who writes stupid jokes, occasionally looks at women with lust in his heart, and thinks Heroes 4 is a decent game. What did you do to deserve this?&rdquo; Suddenly, he gasps and his eyes grow wide with horror, &ldquo;You didn&rsquo;t become an NIMBY, did you!?&rdquo;
&ldquo;No, no! Even I couldn&rsquo;t sink that low,&rdquo; I respond. &ldquo;It all started when I stopped sending Hayden superchats and supporting him on OnlyFans. He didn&rsquo;t take to that very nicely and threw me into a meat grinder, but that didn&rsquo;t actually kill me. I only died because, when Philip got into a car crash, a beer bottle flew out of his hand and through his open window, eventually making contact with my head and killing me instantly. Thankfully, the night before that, I&rsquo;d joined Pastor Jim&rsquo;s Bible Church of East Pensacola. So, I got saved! But, they ain&rsquo;t got no sex in Heaven, and they do have it down here. So, I occasionally mosey on down to the low places for a little, uh, bling bling.&rdquo;
&ldquo;Oh&hellip;okay&hellip;&rdquo; responds Jack, wishing he hadn&rsquo;t asked. &ldquo;Well, either way, I&rsquo;m getting a burning in my bosom which is telling me that Jimmy Wales is the guy I was supposed to save from Heck for my quest, so he&rsquo;s coming with us. You wanna come, Al?&rdquo;
&ldquo;Yeah, sure. They probably have sex in the mortal realm too.&rdquo;
&lt;== Back to Math Problems Home Page &lt;==

Math Problem Thirty-Six: Two True Scotsmen The next circle of Heck looks rather peaceful. When Jack first enters it, nothing seems out of the ordinary. All sees is a pot roasting over a campfire, around which sit Shrek and John Duns Scotus.
&lsquo;Like zoinks!&quot; exclaims Shaggy. &ldquo;Shrek, I was your biggest fan! John Duns Scotus, you were incredibly influential on my understanding of the univocity of theological verbiage! What did you guys do to, like, get darned to Heck!?!?!&rdquo;
&ldquo;Ah, I&rsquo;m happy to have shaped ya intellectual formation lad!&rdquo; says John Duns Scotus, &ldquo;But it ain&rsquo;t us who got our arses darned to Heck.&rdquo;
&ldquo;No laddie,&rdquo; says Shrek, &ldquo;we&rsquo;re true Scotsmen, and the Scots are God&rsquo;s holy and chosen people, so we got saved despite not being part of Pastor Jim&rsquo;s Bible Church of East Pensacola.&rdquo;
&ldquo;But, aren&rsquo;t there like, plenty of Scotsmen who get darned to Heck though?&rdquo;
&ldquo;No true Scot would ever do such a thing!&rdquo; declares John Duns Scotus. &ldquo;He may wear his kilt and read his Glasgow Morning Herald, but he isn&rsquo;t a true Scotsmen! We are the sole true Scotsmen in history (George MacDonald almost made the cut, but he was far too reasonable for Pastor Jim&rsquo;s liking). If only two Scotsmen in the history of Scotland were true Scotsmen, and there have been around 700 million Scotsmen, what percentage of Scotsmen are truly Scotsmen?&rdquo;
&ldquo;Wait a second.&rdquo; Points out Hayden, as observant as he always is, &ldquo;If you bros are saved, then who&rsquo;s in Heck here?&rdquo;
Shrek&rsquo;s face darkens. &ldquo;Ah laddie&hellip;it&rsquo;s the guy in the pot, a sinner so wicked his own circle of Heck was invented to accommodate him!&rdquo; He picks up a spoon, and pulls a screaming rabbit out of the boiling pot.
Soup slides off of its fur, and it is revealed to be none other than Bugs Bunny. His teeth chatter a couple of times.
&ldquo;Nyah, what&rsquo;s up doc?&rdquo;
&ldquo;Oh, shut ya carrot hole!&rdquo; Exclaims Shrek. &ldquo;Scotus is the only lad here who&rsquo;s a doctor in anything, and you weren&rsquo;t even talking to him! Tell these good people what you&rsquo;ve done.&rdquo;
&ldquo;Nyah&hellip;Okay doc, if you&rsquo;re gonna make me&hellip;So, like, I dropped anvils on people, and I blew up some people, and I manufactured many things which are forbidden by the Geneva Convention while I worked at ACME corp.&rdquo;
&lsquo;Fool!&quot; shrieks Shrek, &ldquo;Tell them the rest, tell them the truth!&rdquo;
&ldquo;Nyah&hellip;oh yeah&hellip;&rdquo; the rabbit stammers, clearly overwhelmed by the enormity of his guilt. &ldquo;Once&hellip;I shat on a video game reviewer&rsquo;s face in March of 2011.&rdquo;
His misdeeds exposed, Shrek casts the reprobate rabbit back into his pot with a growl of disgust.
&lt;== Back to Math Problems Home Page &lt;==

Math Problem Thirty - Five: Demons are a Girl&rsquo;s Best Friend As Jack and his ever expanding band of merry men journey their way into the new circle of heck, they hear millions of people throwing up as one. As they come within sight of the darned here, they see a huge mass of pregnant women, all of whom appear to be deep in the throes of morning sickness.
&ldquo;Dear God!&rdquo; exclaims Jack &ldquo;What brought them to this miserable state?&rdquo;
Philip sighs. &ldquo;This is where believers in feminism go - that doctrine which Pastor Jim declared leads women to leave their husbands, kill their babies, practice witchcraft, destroy capitalism, and become lesbians. In service of this false religion, the darned in this circle of Heck refused to be barefoot and pregnant housewives, so now they are forced to be both barefoot and pregnant &hellip; unto eternal ages.
&ldquo;Every woman born after 1993 has bought into feminism &ndash; none of them can cook, all they know is McDonald&rsquo;s. If about half of people are women and two and a half billion people have been born since 1993, how many people will end up here?&rdquo;
&lt;== Back to Math Problems Home Page &lt;==

Math Problem Thirty-Four: Of Grindr and Meat Grinder Relax to these enchanted beats while reading and working out the math problem for a fuller experience. Or cower in fear of them, if you&rsquo;ve played Terraria
Jack and his friends now come upon a lovely, wooded forest. Pixies play in the puddles, alicorns nibble at the grass, and rainbows grace the sky.
&ldquo;Wait a cotton - pickin minute!&rdquo; Exclaims Jack &ldquo;This doesn&rsquo;t look like Heck!&rdquo;
&ldquo;Oh yes, it is.&rdquo; Says Philip &ldquo;This is where gay people and murderers go. Apparently, the powers that be thought that it would be really cruel to force murderers to be in peaceful, enchanted forest forever. Gay people go here because Dante said they went to the same place murderers did a thousand years ago, and nobody bothered to question him since then. The murderers really hate it here, but most of the gay people like it fine.&rdquo;
Then, they see their old friend Hayden there.
&ldquo;HOLY CINNAMON CRUNCH TOAST FUCK!&rdquo; howls Jack &ldquo;HAYDEN, ARE YOU A PRACTICING HOMOSEXUAL!?&rdquo;
Hayden cringes a second and hangs his head in shame. &ldquo;No, I&rsquo;m a murderer.&rdquo;
Jack lets out a sigh of relief and shrugs. &ldquo;Oh, well that&rsquo;s not so bad. How&rsquo;d it happen?&rdquo;
&ldquo;Well, I became a really famous video game streamer before I died, and one of my top super - chatters decided to stop donating, so I threw him into a meat grinder. I was fleeing the scene on my 500 Euro bicycle, and then that Philip hit me full on with his car, although he tried to swerve away, leading him to smash into the car Chase and Kaegan were in. I got darned to Heck because I didn&rsquo;t learn the world was created last Thursday at Pastor Jim&rsquo;s Bible Church of East Pensacola. If my body weighed 195.5 pounds and accelerated away at 172 m / s second after I got hit, how many newtons of force did Philip hit me with?&rdquo;
&lt;== Back to Math Problems Home Page &lt;==

Math Problem Twenty-Eight: Christmas Special! A morbidly obese male ghost appears before Jack, dressed in what appear to be a dirty hospital gown. &ldquo;I am the ghost of Christmas future. Grasp the side of my gown, and you shall see the shape of things to come if your quest is unsuccessful.&rdquo;
Jack thinks about it for a second. &ldquo;Fine, I&rsquo;d like to get out of Heck for a while. It can&rsquo;t be worse than this.&rdquo; So, he obeys the ghost, and his surroundings disappear in a rushing wind. His eyes open to a terrifying scene.
He stands before an open - air stage in Geneva. The sky above the city is the color of a television tuned to a dead channel. The masses around him have been successfully culled. Soy products, vaccines, and Elon Musk&rsquo;s neuralink implants have deprived them of all independent thinking. If their dead, empty eyes are any guide, none of these people can even conceive of sticking their genitalia into KFC deep fryers. Therefore, freedom is dead.
Up onto the stage steps Klaus Schwab - the slanderer, the strongman, the god of this world! In his right hand he holds a pitchfork, in his left a Dungeons and Dragons rulebook. He is arrayed all in black, and his horns can clearly be seen protruding from his head.
He begins to speak. &ldquo;Hello my vondrous underlings, I have an announcement to make to you. Zis night, Santa Klaus - ze inferior Klaus - shall attempt to bring candy canes to ze children. Zis is foolish and unnecessary. Children have no need of candy canes, zey have all ze bugs zey could possibly vant to eat back home in zeir pods.&rdquo;
At this, the crowd goes wild, for eating bugs is the only thing they still have any enthusiasm for, after all these years of being fed their high - fructose corn syrup and denied their horse dewormer. But, the archon raises his hand, and they fall silent.
&ldquo;But afzer tonight, ze inferior Klaus shall bozer us no more. Indeed, I zink I see him coming right over ze city now.&rdquo;
And, the Dark Lord speaks truth. As Jack looks on, a flying red sleigh exits hyperspace 704 feet above the ground. Elon Musk, who has long since forsaken the weakness of his flesh for the cold certainty of steel, is standing 1253 feet due south from Santa. Musk raises his right robotic arm and lets a high intensity laser beam fly at his the jolly old elf. Less than a second later, the sleigh becomes a fireball, and its entourage begin plummeting toward the ground at breakneck speeds. Cries of &ldquo;HO! HO! HO!&rdquo; and &ldquo;WWWWEEEEHHHH!&rdquo; echo throughout Geneva. Assuming that Santa was unable to move any since his exit of hyperspace, and that the intersection of his height and distance from Elon form a right triangle, how much distance did Elon&rsquo;s laser beam have to travel?
&lt;== Back to Math Problems Home Page &lt;==

Math Problem Thirteen: Of Triangles and Taxes One day, Jack walks into his bedroom to find the IRS man standing there, waiting to pounce. He says that Jack&rsquo;s ex-wife owed Bill Clinton 32 trillion dollars in taxes, and that since Jack is marked as her next of kin, he has to pay up. &ldquo;I know you&rsquo;re the god emperor of mankind and all that jazz now,&rdquo; he says, &ldquo;but these are outstanding debts from before that, so you still have to pay up.&rdquo; Jack asks how he came to owe this money, and the tax man heaves a heavy sigh.
&ldquo;Well, after you went to prison, you ex became romantically involved with Bill Clinton. But, their relationship ended on less than favorable terms, and after all that Bill&rsquo;s been through over the past few decades, that was the last straw. He had a psychotic break and assigned large amounts of tax debt to people for arbitrary reasons. In your ex-wife&rsquo;s case, he assigned it based on the area of a certain isosceles triangle.&rdquo;
&ldquo;What? How?&rdquo;
&ldquo;Well, the base of the triangle was 8 trillion units across, but we don&rsquo;t know what its height was. All we know is that its area totalled to 32 trillion units, ergo the 32 trillion dollars you now owe to the IRS.&rdquo;
Jack thought for a second. &ldquo;This sounds phony, like those YouTube ads I get saying that if I click on them beautiful Asian women will have sex with me. If you can tell me what the height of that triangle was, I&rsquo;ll think about paying up, but otherwise you&rsquo;re gonna be in a world of hurt.&rdquo;
The tax man sighed. &ldquo;I was afraid of this. Now I&rsquo;ll have to do math!&rdquo;
&lt;== Back to Math Problems Home Page &lt;==

Math Problem Eleven: The End of the Road The woman accepts Jimmy Wales into her heart as her Lord and Savior and walks away. Suddenly, Jack gets a text on his phone from Jimmy Wales.
&ldquo;You are doing well, son, you have proved yourself to me. Your Wikipedia article shall be stared and featured in rewards for your service.
&ldquo;But, I have a mission for you. Accept, and I shall give you glory beyond your wildest dreams. Reject, and my wrath shall abide upon thee.&rdquo;
Jack thinks for a second, and eventually responds : &ldquo;ay jimmy bro, wikipedia kinda sux ngl fam lamo. ive just found this thing called uncyclopedia thats just like ur website but more better. those fellas got oscar wilde quotes all over the place and you dont bro idk what 2 tell u&rdquo;
For a second, it seems nothing has changed. But then, Jimmy Wales begins typing. &ldquo;How dar&rsquo;st thou speakest in such a vile manner? Thou hast forsaken the one true and holy online encyclopedia project for some shitty comedy outfit. In but a moment, thou shalt know mine fury!&rdquo;
Jack begins to feel a pain in his chest &amp; a sense of impending doom. He knows that Jimmy Wales must have cursed him for his impiety.
The Grim Reaper senses that Jack is going to die, so he starts driving toward Jack in his flying hearse. Of all the souls in the world who need to be harvested, Jack is top priority because he cheated death recently.
If Jack is in Mazatlán, Mexico, and the Grim Reaper is in Elbasan, Albania. The distance between Mazatlán and Elbasan is 6,826 miles. If the Grim Reaper’s flying hearse travels 2,145 miles an hour, how many milliseconds will it be before he reaches Mazatlán?
&lt;== Back to Math Problems Home Page &lt;==

Math Problem Ten: Our Hero Leads a Wayward Fornicator to Faith in Jimmy Wales Jack meets a half - naked woman from the University of California Santa Barbra, premiere party school of the United States. Before Jack even opens his mouth, she offers to have sex with him. Jack wants to very badly, but he knows he must remain chaste for Jimmy Wales.
&ldquo;Why do you let dirty men lust over you day after day?&rdquo; Jack begins. &ldquo;Darling, it doesn&rsquo;t have to be like this. Have you ever used Wikipedia, my darling? This website I use on the daily. Wikipedia is the greatest website you have ever been on, it is the very meaning for life for me. Jimmy Wales made Wikipedia, ransoming us from an eternity of having to pay for library cards! This is a great gift, but there&rsquo;s a catch. Jimmy Wales demands celibacy from us, because sexual intercourse distracts us from editing Wikipedia, and we can&rsquo;t have that.&rdquo;
The promiscuous Californian breaks down and cries. &ldquo;How can I have transgressed so gravely against Jimmy Wales? When I went to Santa Barbra, I was eighteen years old, and then my partying began! Now I&rsquo;m 34, and I&rsquo;m still there, partying as hard as I was the first day! If I spent 8 hours having drunken sex with strangers every day from the minute I got to Santa Barbra, how many hours was I prevented from editing Wikipedia? If I slept with twelve strangers every day and 3% of them had STDS, how many STDs do I have today? Please, Jimmy Wales, have mercy on me!&rdquo;
&lt;== Back to Math Problems Home Page &lt;==
